    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1869-04-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1869-04-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="271" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d271">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Roberts</persName>,
                                    Spanish minister, to Mr. <persName type="to">Fish</persName>,
                                    Secretary of State.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Spain at
                                        Washington</hi>
                    </placeName>,<lb/>
                    <date calendar="gregorian" when="1869-04-15">
                        <hi rend="italic">April</hi> 15,
                                1869</date>.</dateline>
                <p>The minister plenipotentiary of Spain has had the honor to receive
                                the note of 14th instant, in which the honorable Secretary of State
                                pleased to send him copy of a communication from the minister of
                                Peru, dated the 9th, explaining the causes which gave occasion for
                                the touching at Puerto Naranjo, in the island of Cuba, of the
                                Peruvian monitor Manco Capac.</p>
                <p>The undersigned has already sent to his government these satisfactory
                                communications, and presents his thanks to the honorable Secretary
                                Fish for his attention, availing himself of this occasion to offer
                                to him the expression of his highest consideration.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>MAURICIO LOPEZ ROBERTS.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>The Honorable <hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary of
                                        State</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Of the United
                                    States.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
